text: Frommel is the surname of: * Emil Frommel (1828-1896), German theologian and author * Gaston Frommel (1862 - 1906), Swiss theologian, professor of theology * Karl Ludwig Frommel (1789 – 1863), German landscape painter and engraver * Richard Frommel (1854 - 1912), German obstetrician and gynecologist ==See also== * Hyperprolactinaemia, Chiari-Frommel syndrome Category:Surnames
title: Frommel
